LeastUsedSlides_1.label: LeastUsedSlides
LeastUsedSlides_1.query:
q = load "SlidesGenerated";
q = foreach q generate 
    'Id' as 'SlideId',
    'andmoney__1.Name' as 'Template Navn',
    'Name' as 'Slide Navn',
    'andmoney__Subsection_Name__c' as 'Undersektion Navn',
    'andmoney__.Name' as 'Sektionsnavn',
    'final.andmoney__Generated_Slide_Deck__c' as 'GeneratedSlideId', 
    count() as 'Antal Slides';
q = foreach q generate 
    'Template Navn',
    'Slide Navn',
    'Undersektion Navn',
    'Sektionsnavn',
    case 
        when 'GeneratedSlideId' is null then 0
        else sum('Antal Slides')
    end as 'Count';
q = group q by ('Template Navn', 'Slide Navn', 'Sektionsnavn', 'Undersektion Navn');
q = foreach q generate 
    'Template Navn',
    'Slide Navn',
    'Sektionsnavn',
    'Undersektion Navn',
    sum('Count') as 'Antal Slides';
q = order q by 'Antal Slides' asc;
q = limit q 10;

SectionAndSubsection_1.label: SectionAndSubsection
SectionAndSubsection_1.query:
q = load "GeneratedSlidesDataset";
q = foreach q generate 
    'andmoney__1.Name' as 'Section',
    'andmoney__.andmoney__Subsection_Name__c' as 'Subsection',  // Use 'NoSubsection' for null Subsection
    count() as 'CountSlides';
q = group q by ('Section', 'Subsection');
q = foreach q generate 
    'Section' + 
    case
        when ('Subsection' is null) then ""
        else "--"
    end
    +
    coalesce('Subsection', "") as 'SectionSubsection',
    sum('CountSlides') as 'Count';
q = order q by 'Count' desc;  // Sorting by descending count to get the most used first
q = limit q 10;
